00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:54,057
otherwise its battery would influence the resting potential

375
00:24:54,231 --> 00:24:55,557
and it would be more positive,

376
00:24:55,905 --> 00:25:00,380
but because the sodium channels are closed at rest

377
00:25:01,109 --> 00:25:04,747
the battery of the potassium is the dominant battery that

378
00:25:04,919 --> 00:25:09,644
determines the resting potential to a large extent and also

379
00:25:09,843 --> 00:25:13,093
we shall see later, and I just mentioned it at the end

