00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:26,530
these three conductances that I mentioned,

384
00:25:26,764 --> 00:25:28,502
a fast change in the conductance

385
00:25:28,698 --> 00:25:31,304
will change the balance of the batteries or the contribution

386
00:25:31,432 --> 00:25:32,807
of the different batteries.

